summary: PTEN expects selling, general and administrative expenses of $65 million, and depreciation, depletion, amortization and impairment expenses of $230 million for the second quarter.

headline: Oceaneering's Q1 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Rise Y/Y
summary: OII expects full-year 2025 EBITDA to be in the range of $380 million to $430 million and its free cash flow to be between $110 million and $130 million.
